<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="csrf-token" content={get_csrf_token()} />
    <title>Phoenix Static Strapi Example</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      
      .header {
        border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      .nav {
        margin: 1rem 0;
      }
      
      .nav a {
        margin-right: 1rem;
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      
      .nav a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      
      .content {
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }
      
      .post header {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      .post h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      
      .category {
        color: #6c757d;
        font-style: italic;
      }
      
      .category-page header {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      
      .category-page h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      
      .description {
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      
      .blog-index section {
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }
      
      .blog-index h2 {
        color: #495057;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      
      ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
      
      li {
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-left: 3px solid #007bff;
      }
      
      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      
      .category span {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #6c757d;
      }
      
      footer {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Phoenix Static + Strapi CMS Example</h1>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
    
    <main class="content">
      <section class="intro">
        <h2>Welcome!</h2>
        <p>This is a demonstration of how to use <strong>phoenix_static</strong> with Strapi CMS as a content source.</p>
        <p>This example shows how to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fetch content from a Strapi REST API</li>
          <li>Generate static pages for blog posts and categories</li>
          <li>Handle relationships between content types</li>
          <li>Implement proper error handling and fallbacks</li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href="/blog">Visit the blog â†’</a></p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="setup">
        <h2>Setup Instructions</h2>
        <p>To run this example:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Set up a Strapi CMS instance with Posts and Categories collections</li>
          <li>Configure the <code>STRAPI_URL</code> environment variable</li>
          <li>Run <code>mix deps.get</code> to install dependencies</li>
          <li>Start the Phoenix server with <code>mix phx.server</code></li>
        </ol>
        <p>See the README for detailed setup instructions.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>